    <h1>CourseSmart</h1>

    <hr/>
    <h2>Overview and History</h2>

    <p>CourseSmart is a course delivery package that I helped develop for a Software Engineering
      class I took at the University of Vermont. The package is open source and I have started
      to extend the work done by the original development team. It is my hope to perhaps use
      CourseSmart in connection with my VTC classes, either for its own sake or as a sample of a
      fairly extensive client/server system.</p>

    <ul>
      <li>The <a href="index-old.xht">original web page</a> for the project.</li>
    </ul>

