    <p><i>There are no downloads available at this time</i>.</p>

    <h2>Compiling CourseSmart</h2>

    <p>The source code for CourseSmart is available via Subversion at the URL
        <tt>svn://whirlwind.cis.vtc.edu/CourseSmart</tt>.</p>

